2 ) EURO-NET : Network -oriented education and training in a long-term perspective , it is proposed to participate actively in the development of European citizenship through the development of various projects.&#xd;
3 ) EILD -European Institute for Local Development : The European Institute for Local Development holds the role of the secretariat of the European Network for Local Development.&#xd;
Network Every Member has the opportunity to participate on in the projects and Initiatives of the European Network for Local Development. The aim of our activities Networking is the exchange of knowledge and expertise and the joint participation in European and National Initiatives and projects .
